data.description: Everything you need is on this property for living the Coastal lifestyle.    VA Loan assumption allowed.   3/1/2, boatlift w/great fish cleaning area, concrete walkway along the bulkhead, pier, above ground swimming pool, shed with garden area and a self watering system, laundry/utility room downstairs, outdoor shower, boat or truck shed, 2 designated RV connections, fully fenced, nice yard, large concrete driveway, outdoor tv, built-in grill cabinet, mosquito misting system, shed w/garden area and so much more.  THREE minutes to the ICW!!! Close to bait camps, restaurants and Sargent beach.  Want it all, this one has it!
